## Recommended Structure

- `internal/modules/`: domain modules (users, orders, payments, etc.)
- `internal/middleware/`: HTTP middlewares
- `internal/guards/`: access guards
- `internal/events/`: publishers/subscribers
- `internal/checkers/`: health checks
- `internal/scheduler/`: jobs and schedulers
- `internal/hooks/`: shutdown hooks

